arts.ttl: Villarreal wins at Valencia to strengthen hold on 3rd place in La Liga
arts.sum: Villarreal trails leader Real Madrid by four points and second-placed Barcelona by two before the front-runners meet in a clasico match in the capital on Sunday. A last-gasp goal snatched a point for Real Oviedo after a wild 3-3 draw at Girona in a meeting of the two bottom clubs.
